          <h3>Open Source (coming soon!)</h3>
          <p>The open-source edition of Spark comes with all of the features included in the cloud version. Spark is best hosted on a L*MP stack - full system specification are being writter, but you can expect them to be very similar to the system requirements
            for <a href="https://www.drupal.org/docs/7/system-requirements" target="_blank">Drupal 7</a>.</p>
          <p>We are currently working out a few bugs to make updating and upgrading as seemless as possible so that you can easily update your version of Spark</p>
